.START 

Gerald H. Blum was named vice chairman and director of marketing and merchandise direction at this retailer, a newly created post.
The move is effective Feb. 1.
Until April, Mr. Blum had been executive vice president and director of marketing and research for Lord & Taylor, a unit of May Department Stores Co.
He has been, and until Jan. 31 will remain, a consultant for Lord & Taylor. 

